There was one other sighting in Honiton on or around February 2nd 2010
divs: Sighting DetailsWe were walking home from Tesco when we saw some strange light at the top of Roundball Hill it was a blueish colour we thought it was just a torch light but then it shoot up and hovered for a while then it split into two and circled the top of the hill and clashed back together and pulsated an orange colour then shot straight up out of sight.
